I [[Assign Static Ip Addres on Nixos]] to "192.168.1.20" because I use this machine also as rustdesk relay.

``` nix
rustdesk-server = {
  enable = true;
  openFirewall = true;
  signal.relayHosts = [ "192.168.1.20" ];
};

systemd.services.rustdesk-signal.environment.ALWAYS_USE_RELAY = "Y";
```
